newest.message:
== Contributors for this version ==
* Jimi * SyndicateAexeron * Quantix Blackstar * Travis Puderbaugh * Kunnis Niam
== Bug Fixes == * Fixed possible crash bug when EVEMon loads the Certificates data file. * Fixed Character After Plan Export. * Fixed a bug where the Naglfar, Talwar, Corax, Algos and Dragoon race were set as "Faction". * Fixed date and time parsing in Scheduler when using custom date and time formatting.
== Enhancements == * EVEMon now supports any date time format.
== Misc == * Blueprint copies will no longer be included in assets total estimated value. * Several improvements have been done to the base code to make EVEMon a better application.
